, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(3, 18, 26); display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; flex: 1 1 0%;\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(104, 113, 118); text-align: center;\">Lưu/chụp lại màn hình gồm mã QR code, dòng ghi họ tên, ngày khởi hành và số hiệu chuyến bay.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"css-1dbjc4n r-knv0ih\" style=\"border: 0px solid black; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 8px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; -webkit-box-align: stretch; -webkit-box-direction: normal; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; align-items: stretch; display: flex; flex-basis: auto; flex-direction: column; flex-shrink: 0; min-height: 0px; min-width: 0px; position: relative; z-index: 0; white-space: normal;\"><div dir=\"auto\" class=\"css-901oao r-13awgt0 r-1sixt3s r-majxgm r-fdjqy7\" style=\"border: 0px solid black; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: MuseoSans, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(3, 18, 26); display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; flex: 1 1 0%;\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Trường hợp bạn không khai báo y tế điện tử t